des: My flash briefing is about delivering valuable content to my community. I will share my thoughts on certain business categories, predominantly categories with a real estate focus (yes, I'm a realtor). I'll also be putting out food recommendations, local events, places to go in the Auburn and Opelika area, my Jeep escapades, and my awesome family.
